Step 1: Start.
Step 2: Initialise an array box[] with the capacity of each carton.
Step 3: Accept a number n and make a copy nn.
Step 4: Verify whether the number is out of range
Step 5: If step 4 is true stop.
Step 6: Using a for loop divide n by element at i.
Step 7: If step 6 equals to 0  print the results required and stop, or else go to step 8
Step 8: Find remainder when n is divided with the element at i.
Step 9: Add the value of n divided by element at i.
Step 10: Repeat steps 6-9.
Step 11: Stop.
